*********IMPORTANT INFO ************
I ship by weight !!! I try to ship in polybags as boxes make packages heavier, thus increasing the price... however I do ship by weight as required on the Vinted site 
*****a small bundle only goes up to 0.5 ounces which is barely the weight of one small lightweight shirt  so this cannot be negotiated it’s not my choice it’s the rules of Vinted and the rules of the post office so if you order a large bundle and I choose the small shipping when I go to the post office they will not ship it they will make me pay more money right then and there or else they will not ship it so please don’t ask to get the shipping size smaller because I always choose the shipping that coincides with the weight and while it is possible to get away with going over weight a time or two it’s not worth the risk to have to lose the money and have to pay shipping twice or make the customer pay more before the post office will release their package so I’d rather play it safe and do what I’m supposed to do and I have had to pay shipping twice bedore due to improper shipping size so please dont ask *********i Price my items Extremely low to help offset the cost of shipping a lot of my items are only a dollar so please keep that in mind**********

Hello friends ! I’m a single mommy aka superwoman.  I love this site cuz its fun and saves me money ! I post new stuff often, I love to swap and I m very flexible with prices and swapping so just ask about anything you like and I will work with you to make it yours ! Everything ordered is mailed out within 3 days and usually within 24 hours ... I like to move my items fast so if something of mine doesn't sell fast, it will most likely be reduced.  Also, if for any reason at all you are unhappy with your purchase pleaseee let me know ASAP and I will make it right for you.  Please dont leave me negative feedback  without giving me a chance to make you happy ! Find me on fb lets be friends facebook.com/justloveme777
